Empathic Link									CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality			VISIBLE:YES	DESC:The master has an empathic link with his familiar to a distance of 1 mile. The master cannot see through the familiar's eyes, but they can communicate empathically. Because of the limited nature of the link, only general emotions can be communicated. As a result, the master has the same connection to an item or place that his familiar does.																																					SOURCEPAGE:p.
